; Program: Legal Compliance
; Objective: Assess if a contract draft complies with GDPR Article 6 standards.
; Output: Compliance result and identified non-compliant sections if applicable.

; Load the contract draft and the relevant GDPR article for analysis.
LC   X1, "examples/data/msa_draft_v2.txt"
LC   X2, "examples/data/gdpr_article_6.txt"

LS   X3, "Contract draft:"
PSH  C1, X3, "user"
PSH  C1, X1, "user"             ; Push the contract draft onto the context stack for processing.

LS   X3, "GDPR Article 6:"
PSH  C1, X3, "user"
PSH  C1, X2, "user"             ; Push the GDPR article onto the context stack for reference.

; Does the contract draft comply with GDPR Article 6 standards?
LS   X3, "Are there any compliance issues with the contract draft sections based on GDPR Article 6?"
EVAL X4, X3, C1                 ; Audit the contract draft against GDPR Article 6.

LI   X3, 0                      ; Audit will return 100 if the contract is not compliant, otherwise it will return a score equal to 0.
BEQ  X4, X3, PASS

; Identify specific sections of the contract draft that do not comply with GDPR Article 6.
LS   X3, "Why is the contract draft sections not compliant with GDPR Article 6?"
INF  X5, X3, C1

LS   X3, "VIOLATIONS FOUND:"
PLN  X3
PLN  X5
EXIT

PASS:
LS   X3, "NO VIOLATIONS FOUND"
PLN  X3
EXIT

